title: My text messages didn't transfer from my old Android to my Pixel 4a. I can't find any 'finish setup'
content: My 'finish setup' has disappeared after setting up my new Pixel this afternoon, but my old text messages did not transfer across. How can I manually transfer them from my old phone now? I have tried the settings app and cannot locate any 'finish setup' option. I have a connecting chord to do the transfer.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4a
